---
title: Teriyaki Pork Bowl & Peanut Rice with Coconut Sweet Chilli Sauce & Pickled Cucumber
description: Get ready for an Asian-inspired meal that comes together in a flash. If you’re a lover of sweet, zesty and umami, then you’re going to love this teriyaki pork and veggie bowl bursting with colour and flavour. Bonus: the peanut rice adds loads of texture so that every bite has that crunch factor!
